Canonical website:
  https://github.com/OpenSC/pkcs11-helper/

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/OpenSC/pkcs11-helper/archive/refs/tags/pkcs11-helper-1.30.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack pkcs11-helper-1.30.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./pkcs11-helper-1.30.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/pkcs11-helper-1.30.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/pkcs11-helper-1.30.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libpkcs11-helper1-1.30.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libpkcs11-helper-devel-1.30.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

